This paper deals with the problem of metric learning, which is a common topic in machine learning and falls under the category of "Learning" (cs.LG). The paper specifically focuses on multi-view data, which involves multiple sources of information, such as images and text, and can be analyzed using computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of kernel methods, which are commonly used in multimedia analysis (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, and cs.MM, in that order.
